  "title": "<div><br></div>",
  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Each week, students may acquire weapons, armor, and artifacts from literature.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each week, one weapon, one armor, and three literary artifacts will be available.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each artifact has a one-time effect but may come with hidden consequences.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Once taken, an item cannot be used by another player.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> Example: Week 4 (Gothic Horror &amp Madness)</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Category</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Item</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect</div>",
